- SONGKRAN PARTY is a 5-reel, 4-row video slot featuring Free Spins Feature.

-During any spin, when 1 or more Stacked Wild symbols appear fully on any reels, all wins for that spin will be multiplied by those Stacked Wild symbols' corresponding multipliers.

-A stacked Wild symbol appearing fully on reels 1, 2, 3, 4, and 5 awards x1, x2, x3, x4, and x5 multiplier respectively. When Stacked Wild symbols occupy all of the reels, 5000x of the total bet amount is awarded.

- The game is played with 20 base bets for 243 ways, bet levels of 1 to 10, and bet sizes of 0.01 to 0.25.

- The Bet Size is set using the "bet Size" selector.

- The Bet Level is set using the "bet Level" selector.

- The Bet Amount is set using the "Bet Amoun" selector.

- "Cash Wallet" displays the cash available for wager.

- "Auto Spin" automatically the cash available for wager.

- Winning combinations and payouts are made according to the "Paytable".

- A bet way win in cash is equal to the value shown in the "Paytable" multiplied by the bet size and bet level.

- Bet ways win if the winning symbols are in succession from the leftmost reel to right.

- A total number of winning bet ways for each symbol is calculated by multiplying the number of adjacent winning symbols on each symbol from the leftmost reel to right.

- The winning symbol payout is multiplied by the number of winning bet ways.

- Simultaneous wins on different bet ways are added.

- All wins show in cash.

- Wild symbol substitutes for all symbols except the Free Spins symbol.

- Wild symbol appears on reels 2, 3, and 4 only.

- Free Spins Feature is played at the same bet size and bet level as the spin that triggered the Free Spins Feature.

- 3, 4, or 5 Scatter symbols appearing anywhere will trigger the Free Spins Feature with 8, 12, or 20 free spins respectively.

- When 1 or more Stacked Wild symbols appear partially on any reels during any free spins, the Stacked Wild symbol(s) will be nudged into its reels fully. Free spins can be retriggered.

Spin
Tap to start spin at the current Base Bet, bet Size and Bet Level.
Tap the button or the game area during a spin to stop the reels.
Press the <Space> key to start spin at the current Base Bet, bet Size and Bet Level (applicable to PC version only)
Press and Hold <Space> key will continue game spins until it is released. (applicable to PC version only)
